cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a transfer learning method for deep neural networks and applies it to image classification for sepsis. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves the use of deep learning and artificial intelligence, which further supports the likelihood of it belonging to cs.AI. The method proposed in the paper involves the transfer of all parameters of a DNN, which suggests that it may also be relevant to the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the paper applies the method to two-dimensional electrophoresis image classification, which suggests that it may also be relevant to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
